#: cracknuts.acquisition.acquisition.Acquisition.do:3 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The returned dictionary should contain ``plaintext`` and ``ciphertext`` "
"keys and may optionally include ``key`` and ``extended`` keys. The "
"plaintext is the data to be encrypted, the ciphertext is the encrypted "
"result, the key is used to encrypt the plaintext, and the extended field "
"is for any custom data you want to save. Expected structure: "
"``{\"plaintext\": bytes, \"ciphertext\": bytes, \"key\": bytes, "
"\"extended\": bytes}``."
msgstr ""
"返回的字典应包含 ``plaintext`` 和 ``ciphertext`` 键，可选包含 ``key`` 和 ``extended`` "
"键。plaintext 是待加密的数据，ciphertext 是加密结果，key 用于加密明文，extended "
"字段用于保存任意自定义数据。期望结构：``{\"plaintext\": bytes, \"ciphertext\": bytes, "
"\"key\": bytes, \"extended\": bytes}``。"

#: cracknuts.acquisition.acquisition.Acquisition.do:10 of
